In the name of Allah

Salaam,

This is an effort to extract data and metadata out of NoorSoft's products,
and create better programs using those resources.

You may help in several ways:

 * Write program on already-extracted data,
 * Reverse-engineer your favorite product of NoorSoft, and share the results,
   including the experience,
 * Document the work already done,
 * Spread the word

Let's put an end to monopoly of NoorSoft in religious software market for the
sake of Allah :)
